# Menus - KX Delta Platform

Original URL: https://code.kx.com/platform/menus/

## File

The _File_ menu items create various entities

![Screenshot](../img/control/filemenu.png)

The _Tools_ menu contains links to [_KX
Analyst_](https://code.kx.com/analyst/), [_KX
Dashboards_](https://code.kx.com/dashboards/), package control, the
[Viewers](../viewers/), and the console log.

![Screenshot](../img/control/toolsmenu.jpg)

item | action  
---|---  
Connect to Control | Open _KX Analyst_ (if running) on Control Process  
Open Viewer | Select and open a viewer  
Open Builder | Open _KX Dashboards_ or _KX Analyst_ (if running)  
Open Control Partial Log | Open up the Control log file  
Open Package Importer | Open Package Importer  
Open Package Exporter | Open Package Exporter  
Show Console | Display console log window  
  
