KX Control | Documentation for _KX Control_  
KX Monitoring | Documentation for _KX Monitoring_  
KX Stream | Documentation for _KX Stream_  
Process Template API | Documentation for _Process Templates_  
License Information | ![Screenshot](../img/control/licenseinformation.jpg)  
![screenshot](../img/control/licensesummary.jpg)  
![screenshot](../img/control/xmlfile.jpg)  
  
## User

The _User_ menu is on the right side of the window.

![Screenshot](../img/control/administrator.png)

item | action  
---|---  
Theme | Switch between Light and Dark Theme  
Language | Choose between English, German, Japanese, Arabic  
Change Password | Change log-in password. Once changed, you will be logged out and returned to the login screen  
About | Show the version information. Useful for providing license, runtime and other info for reporting  
![Screenshot](../img/control/versioninformation.png)  
Logout | Log out of _KX Control_

